text: Ennetmoos is a municipality in the canton of Nidwalden in Switzerland. The main sights of Ennetmoos are the chapels of Saint Jakob, Saint Leonhard (in Rohren), and Saint Magnus (in Allweg), a monument (Ãœberfalldenkmal) in Allweg, ruins at Rotzberg, the Stanserhorn mountain and resort, and the pilgrimage route St. Jakobsweg. == References == ==Other websites== *Official Homepage of Ennetmoos Category:Municipalities of Nidwalden
